rd contacted me with some very vague promises regarding the future. I pressed him to tell me what they were but he refused, saying they were secret at this time and he couldnt say, but he urged me to 'wait a month and see'.<br><br>As the 'month' now exceeds the time we have left on the existing gold subscription, I asked him for an extension... he responded saying he would use the funds currently in the community chest ($306) towards any necessary extension of the gold subscription... seeing as I was considering relocating which would have meant those funds were perminantly lost anyway, I have decided to wait and see.<br><br>Once ezboard announce what they grand plan for the eq community are, I will put up a poll and we will make a decision as an entire communtiy.<br><br>Zadkiel. <p><TABLE BORDER=0 ALIGN=CENTER><TR ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN=MIDDLE><TD ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN=MIDDLE><A HREF="mailto:zadkiel@monkly-business.com"><IMG SRC="http://www.btinternet.com/~wulf/zadkielsig.jpg"></A></TD></TR></TABLE></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uzadkiel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zadkiel</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0> at: 9/19/02 3:30:59 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ufyrrwin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fyrrwin</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Grand Master</span><br>  Posts: 1056<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/19/02 6:44:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32147.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Monkly Business and ezboard.</span><hr size=1> Hmmmm...I'm interested to hear what EZboard is planning. <br><br>This sounds like a good plan for n